Right Click on the target application .exe file
Click "Send to"
Click "Desktop (create shortcut)

Go to the Desktop, right click to the shortcut file
Click "Properties"
Change "Target" field to the below: (remember to replace "%userprofile%\Desktop\example.exe" to your application path)
cmd /min /C "set __COMPAT_LAYER=RUNASINVOKER && start "" "%userprofile%\Desktop\example.exe""
